  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>About This Game</strong></li></ul>This game is BackRoomsNew in game after each level the game will be more difficult and in each level there will be all kinds of monsters that will try to catch you.<br>All levels are mazes from which you have to escape and when you escape it will be another maze again.<br>Each level will have a task where you have to find a key or lever and various items to open the door, but some levels only require finding the exit, such as level 0.<br>Made in Lithuania Palanga.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>FEATURES</strong></li></ul>Multiplayer<br>Virtual Reality<br>Proximity Voice Chat<br>New Levels (current level 10)<br>GameModes only in mutliplayer<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>GameModes</strong></li></ul>Survival <br>Run And Escape<br>(you can write in discord what gamemode should i add)<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Questions</strong></li></ul>Join Discord if you find bug or have some questions<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095330/extras/d0707d96636ec2caade6fe382785165f.poster.avif?t=1713974950\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095330/extras/d0707d96636ec2caade6fe382785165f.webm?t=1713974950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095330/extras/d0707d96636ec2caade6fe382785165f.mp4?t=1713974950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Matas was here xoxo<br>Bodybuilder Faustas",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>About This Game</strong></li></ul>This game is BackRoomsNew in game after each level the game will be more difficult and in each level there will be all kinds of monsters that will try to catch you.<br>All levels are mazes from which you have to escape and when you escape it will be another maze again.<br>Each level will have a task where you have to find a key or lever and various items to open the door, but some levels only require finding the exit, such as level 0.<br>Made in Lithuania Palanga.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>FEATURES</strong></li></ul>Multiplayer<br>Virtual Reality<br>Proximity Voice Chat<br>New Levels (current level 10)<br>GameModes only in mutliplayer<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>GameModes</strong></li></ul>Survival <br>Run And Escape<br>(you can write in discord what gamemode should i add)<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Questions</strong></li></ul>Join Discord if you find bug or have some questions<br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095330/extras/d0707d96636ec2caade6fe382785165f.poster.avif?t=1713974950\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095330/extras/d0707d96636ec2caade6fe382785165f.webm?t=1713974950\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2095330/extras/d0707d96636ec2caade6fe382785165f.mp4?t=1713974950\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Matas was here xoxo<br>Bodybuilder Faustas",
